parameters:
You cannot escape from the dungeon until you clear the
quest. Will you still proceed?
Thief Nora: I can hear noises... It's getting noisy outside.
Thief Nora: Let's proceed to the depths of the cave!
Captain Clevo: Are you telling me to betray my comrades!?

Captain Clevo: Are you telling us to become scum worse than
thieves, demeaning our oath and comrades!?

Veteran member of the Emma Thief Guild: If I may speak,
Captain! The Emma Thief Guild is on the verge of collapse...

Veteran member of the Emma Thief Guild: The young members
who grew tired of the captain's ideals acted on their own
and were all killed...

Veteran member of the Emma Thief Guild: Some members, in
order to survive, have started looting without choosing
their targets.

Veteran member of the Emma Thief Guild: There are few who
are willing to die for the ideology of reclaiming land from
the nobles...

Veteran member of the Emma Thief Guild: We're already just
ordinary thieves. We're the only ones who still think of
ourselves as righteous thieves...

Captain Clevo: Who are you... and how did you manage to
bypass the security?

Veteran member of the Emma Thief Guild: I called for them.
This person is the one I made contact with in Oros.
Captain Clevo: You... don't tell me you're suggesting that--

Psema the Fake Adventurer: There is a noble who is willing
to cooperate with us in Oros.

Psema the Fake Adventurer: I have quite a peculiar hobby,
you see. I absolutely love dealing with beings other than
humans.
Captain Clevo: If you say any more, I'll kill you.

Psema the Fake Adventurer: Please don't misunderstand. I
just came here to propose a way to survive in this desperate
situation.

Psema the Fake Adventurer: Ahaha, it's now a matter of
choosing between two options, whether to protect your ideal
of the Emma Thief Guild...

Psema the Fake Adventurer: Or perhaps you'd prefer to sell
off the beastwoman Nora.

Fake Adventurer Psema: Well, Captain Clevo of the Emma Thief
Guild, which one will you choose...?
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Emma, a member of the thief gang: Where did you come
from!?... Wait, could it be...

Emma, a member of the thief gang, says If I remember
correctly... you're the leader, right?
